<L>At la&s;t two Javelins &s;ent from lucky Hands</L>
<L>In both his fiery threatning Eyes did light,</L>
<L>Depriving him, though not of &s;trength, of &s;ight;</L>
<L>Who&s;e yet blind rage draws many a ruin on,</L>
<L>Until at la&s;t a huge and ma&s;&s;y Stone,</L>
<L>Shot from a Bulwark-battering Engine &s;troke</L>
